<div id="bordeaux-static-slot-7" class="bordeaux-slot" data-feat-ref="bordeaux-feat-id-200"></div>
<p>To help you reach this editing nirvana, we&#8217;ve selected the best video editing software available today, bar none. We have software at a range of budgets, and for Windows PCs, Mac and Android devices. (If you&#8217;re <em>only </em>interested in mobile apps, though, then our guide to the best video editing apps will serve you better.)</p>
