<div id="bordeaux-static-slot-8" class="bordeaux-slot" data-feat-ref="bordeaux-feat-id-201"></div>
<p>Whether you&#8217;re a professional working on movies and streaming content, a YouTube trying to make your footage sing, or just an enthusiastic smartphone user wanted to make your holiday clips look slick, you&#8217;ll find the right tool for your needs here. Of course, along with the best video editing software, you&#8217;re going to want the best hardware. So don&#8217;t miss our guides to the best monitors for video editing, the best laptops for video editing and the best tablets for video editing.</p>
<div id="bordeaux-static-slot-9" class="bordeaux-slot" data-feat-ref="bordeaux-feat-id-202"></div>
<p>Right now, though, scroll down to find quick links to today&#8217;s top 3 deals, followed by our full dive into the best video editing software.</p>
